item.title: 【Albums (lossless)】FLAC - NCT 126 - Fact Check (Qobuz FLAC 24bit/96kHz)
item.description:
Fact Check is the fifth full-length album by NCT 127. It was released on October 6, 2023 with "Fact Check" serving as the album's title track.

The physical album comes in 22 versions: Chandelier version, Storage version, nine Exhibit versions, retail exclusive Exhibit version, nine SMini versions and QR version.
